00:29:02,640 --> 00:29:04,529
You can
even hypnotize people over the phone.

574
00:29:04,720 --> 00:29:07,246
Some big tours
around the U.S. for a few years,

575
00:29:07,320 --> 00:29:09,322
- two TV specials.
